yle or application of her skill set in places where it isn’t directly</div><div class="t m0 x23 h12 ya4 ff9 fsd fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">178 <span class="_ _12"> </span>| <span class="_ _12"> </span>THE MANAGER’<span class="_ _8"></span>S P<span class="_ _b"></span>A<span class="_ _0"></span>TH</div><a class="l" href="#pf73" data-dest-detail='[115,"XYZ",null,542.16,null]'><div class="d m1" style="border-style:none;position:absolute;left:451.811366px;bottom:733.483773px;width:42.772510px;height:10.000000px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.000001);"></div></a><a class="l" href="#pfc2" data-dest-detail='[194,"XYZ",null,80,null]'><div class="d m1" style="border-style:none;position:absolute;left:729.501505px;bottom:648.176690px;width:3.168000px;height:6.000000px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.000001);"></div></a></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[2.314815,0.000000,0.000000,2.314815,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
